columns.name: name
columns.description: A globally unique name for the container registry.

columns.name: created_at
columns.description: A time value given in ISO8601 combined date and time format that represents when the registry was created.

columns.name: storage_usage_bytes
columns.description: The amount of storage used in the registry in bytes.

columns.name: storage_usage_bytes_updated_at
columns.description: The time at which the storage usage was updated. Storage usage is calculated asynchronously, and may not immediately reflect pushes to the registry.

columns.name: urn
columns.description: The uniform resource name (URN) for the container registry.
